    • Method Detail

      • createSourceInfo

        public SourceInfo createSourceInfo(String type,
                                   String reference,
                                   PropertyValue date,
                                   String description)
        Creates and returns a SourceInfo containing type, reference, date, and descriptive information about the source of some data.
        Parameters:
        type - A String containing the type of the source of the data, or null to specify no type.
        reference - A String containing the reference of the source of the data, or null to specify no reference.
        date - A PropertyValue containing the date of the source of data (generated using PropertyValueFactory), or null to specify no date.
        description - A String containing a description of the source of the data, or null to specify no description.
        Returns:
        See above.
